<section class="privacy-container">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>

    <p>
        This Privacy Policy outlines how your data is collected, used, and protected when using the <strong>Student Management</strong> system.
    </p>

    <h3>Information We Collect</h3>
    <p>
        The application stores personal and academic information about students, including:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Full name</li>
        <li>Gender</li>
        <li>Date of birth</li>
        <li>GPA</li>
        <li>Profile image (if uploaded)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>How We Use the Data</h3>
    <p>
        The collected data is used solely for academic record management and demonstration purposes within the system. The information is not shared with third parties.
    </p>

    <h3>Data Storage</h3>
    <p>
        All student information is stored securely in a SQL Server database. Uploaded images are stored on the server and associated with the respective student records.
    </p>

    <h3>Security</h3>
    <p>
        We implement basic security practices to prevent unauthorized access. However, this is a demo application and not intended for production use without additional security hardening.
    </p>

    <h3>Your Consent</h3>
    <p>
        By using this system, you consent to the collection and use of information as outlined in this policy.
    </p>

    <h3>Contact</h3>
